{"id":2605,"date":"2023-08-26T15:33:48","date_gmt":"2023-08-26T08:33:48","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/?p=2605"},"modified":"2023-10-02T10:43:06","modified_gmt":"2023-10-02T03:43:06","slug":"chung-minh-thay-gi-trong-ngay-hoi-nhap-hoc-tai-truong-dai-hoc-thanh-do-2023","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/chung-minh-thay-gi-trong-ngay-hoi-nhap-hoc-tai-truong-dai-hoc-thanh-do-2023\/","title":{"rendered":"CH\u00daNG M\u00ccNH TH\u1ea4Y G\u00cc TRONG NG\u00c0Y H\u1ed8I NH\u1eacP H\u1eccC T\u1ea0I TR\u01af\u1edcNG \u0110\u1ea0I H\u1eccC TH\u00c0NH \u0110\u00d4 2023"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>Th\u1ea5y \u00e1nh m\u1eaft tin t\u01b0\u1edfng<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong> c\u1ee7a b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9<\/strong> theo t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c T\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean K15. <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Ngay t\u1eeb s\u1edbm, c\u00e1c ph\u1ee5 huynh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c T\u00e2n Thadoers \u1edf xa \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 \u0111\u1ec3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc, tham quan v\u00e0 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1c Th\u1ea7y C\u00f4 gi\u00e1o, T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n vi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n c\u00e1c b\u1eadc Ph\u1ee5 huynh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c T\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc. Nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm, nh\u1eefng n\u00e9t m\u1eb7t kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00f2 m\u00f2, nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebfng tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1eadc ph\u1ee5 huynh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n sinh vi\u00ean t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng trong ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_17708\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-17708\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-17708 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/IMG_9814-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-17708\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Ph\u1ee5 huynh \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1edbm l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc cho T\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean K15<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>Th\u1ea5y b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong> nh\u1ed9n nh\u1ecbp, h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng, kh\u1ea9n tr\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/strong> trong c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc. Ngay t\u1eeb s\u00e1ng s\u1edbm kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed t\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng n\u00e1o nhi\u1ec7t b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m t\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5 huynh \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb kh\u1eafp n\u01a1i h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u00ed sinh, qu\u00fd ph\u1ee5 huynh t\u1eeb c\u00e1c t\u1ec9nh xa nh\u01b0 \u0110i\u1ec7n Bi\u00ean, Lai Ch\u00e2u,..hay c\u00e1c t\u1ec9nh \u0111\u00e3 &#8220;check-in&#8221; t\u1ea1i Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 t\u1eeb s\u00e1ng s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb n\u01a1i \u1edf cho con trong th\u1eddi gian 4 n\u0103m h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3n ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t, kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed r\u1ed9n r\u00e0ng, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i tham quan quanh Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, khu v\u1ef1c k\u00fd t\u00fac x\u00e1, khu gi\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, ph\u00f2ng th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh,\u00a0 c\u00e1c T\u00e2n Sinh vi\u00ean b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c, mong ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ea7y &#8220;s\u1eafc m\u00e0u&#8221; trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_17696\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-17696\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-17696 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/4-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-17696\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u00f9ng T\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean d\u00e0nh th\u1eddi gian d\u1ea1o quanh khu\u00f4n vi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc n\u0103m 2023, ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u00e1c \u201c\u00fat c\u01b0ng\u201d l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Thado-er ch\u00ednh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra trong kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed n\u00f4 n\u1ee9c, h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>Th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m chu \u0111\u00e1o<\/b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>c\u1ee7a b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9, th\u1ea7y c\u00f4.<\/strong> V\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c tr\u00ean t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i c\u1ee7a con, mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng tin c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o cho con trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian theo h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1eddng, nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n t\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean l\u00ean nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc c\u00f9ng c\u1ea3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh trong ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t n\u00e0y.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u00e2u \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn nghe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1eadc ph\u1ee5 huynh v\u1ec1 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc, tr\u0103n tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 n\u01a1i \u1edf, th\u1eddi gian h\u1ecdc, ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n \u0111i l\u1ea1i, tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i kh\u00f4ng\u2026 \u0110\u00fang l\u00e0, d\u00f9 c\u00f3 l\u1edbn v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y th\u00e1ng r\u1eddi xa v\u00f2ng tay b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1ea1i m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9 th\u00ec c\u00e1c con v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n b\u00e9 b\u1ecfng, c\u1ea7n ch\u1edf che.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_17698\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-17698\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-17698 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/5-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-17698\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed nh\u1ed9n nh\u1ecbp t\u1ea1i khu v\u1ef1c l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chu \u0111\u00e1o s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n t\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean. N\u0103m nay ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00e1t huy nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u quy tr\u00ecnh nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a sinh vi\u00ean.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><em>\u2207<\/em>\u00a0Xem th\u00eam chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/huong-dan-nhap-hoc-truc-tuyen-tai-truong-dai-hoc-thanh-do\"><em>C\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4<\/em><\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Quy tr\u00ecnh nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o qua c\u00e1c k\u00eanh th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a Nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng, c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn chi ti\u1ebft nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c th\u1ea7y c\u00f4, c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n vi\u00ean v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n t\u00ecnh nguy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap ph\u1ee5 huynh v\u00e0 t\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean nhanh ch\u00f3ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u00e0 nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc theo \u0111\u00fang quy tr\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>Th\u1ea5y m\u00e0u s\u1eafc vui nh\u1ed9n, n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">,<\/span><b> nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> t\u1eeb c\u00e1c anh ch\u1ecb sinh vi\u00ean kh\u00f3a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho c\u00e1c c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9. Khu\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng m\u00e0u s\u1eafc \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng C\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9. T\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean th\u00edch th\u00fa quan t\u00e2m nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n c\u00f2n nhanh ch\u00f3ng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u00e0 ghi danh m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 y\u00eau th\u00edch.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_17704\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-17704\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-large wp-image-17704\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/IMG_0095-1-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-17704\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean ghi danh v\u00e0o CLB y\u00eau th\u00edch<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>Th\u1ea5y ni\u1ec1m tin, ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng mong ch\u1edd<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp m\u1edbi, g\u1eb7p th\u1ea7y c\u00f4 m\u1edbi, b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb h\u00e0nh trang b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o n\u0103m th\u00e1ng m\u1edbi. C\u1ea7m tr\u00ean tay \u0111\u1ed3ng ph\u1ee5c sinh vi\u00ean c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc si\u00eau \u201ch\u1eefu d\u1ee5ng\u201d T\u00e2n Thadoers h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00f3n ch\u1edd nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u00fa v\u1ecb s\u1eafp t\u1edbi d\u01b0\u1edbi m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 chung Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-17720\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/IMG_0048-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sau khi c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m chu\u1ea9n x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n, t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 26\/08\/2023, tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c <\/span><b>Ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc: \u201cOpen day 2023\u201d<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n t\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc m\u1ed9t chi\u1ec1u di\u1ec5n ra nhanh ch\u00f3ng, thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n, \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc t\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1eadn t\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Th\u1ea7y C\u00f4, c\u00e1c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n vi\u00ean v\u00e0 anh ch\u1ecb sinh vi\u00ean ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c li\u00ean quan, nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin chung v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea7n qu\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc, c\u00e1c T\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng cung c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 M\u00e3 s\u1ed1 sinh vi\u00ean, t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u0103ng nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ed5ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng th\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0 t\u00e0i nguy\u00ean tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_17706\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-17706\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-17706 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/IMG_9813-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-17706\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1n b\u1ed9 ph\u00f2ng C\u00f4ng t\u00e1c sinh vi\u00ean h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 l\u1ecbch h\u1ecdc, k\u00fd t\u00fac x\u00e1, ph\u00f2ng tr\u1ecd t\u1edbi c\u00e1c T\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean <\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng trang b\u1ecb khu k\u00fd t\u00fac x\u00e1 v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 th\u00f4ng tin nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh d\u00e0nh cho sinh vi\u00ean c\u00f3 nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng \u1edf k\u00fd t\u00fac x\u00e1, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5 huynh an t\u00e2m tin t\u01b0\u1edfng g\u1eedi g\u1eafm con theo h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i Tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Ngo\u00e0i ra, th\u1ea7y c\u00f4 Ph\u00f2ng c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c sinh vi\u00ean c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i sinh vi\u00ean t\u00ecnh nguy\u1ec7n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cung c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c khu ph\u00f2ng tr\u1ecd v\u0103n minh, an to\u00e0n thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n xung quanh khu v\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng, nh\u1eb1m h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean \u1edf xa c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ed7 \u1edf.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">H\u00f4m nay l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong chu\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n T\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean K15, \u0111\u1ee3t 1 nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc k\u00e9o d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ebfn 5\/9\/2023. Nh\u1eafc nh\u1eb9 l\u00e0 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n vi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1eddng Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c xuy\u00ean L\u1ec5, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1eddng trong d\u1ecbp l\u1ec5 v\u00e0 nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00f3 nha.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\"><em><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u2207<\/span> D\u1ea1o quanh m\u1ed9t v\u00f2ng qua nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m \u1ea3nh m\u00e0 ch\u00fang m\u00ecnh ghi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong <a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/drive\/u\/4\/folders\/1iSa6N3Gyl3pPMr8H36JOucERPWuGsk9x\"><strong>Ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4<\/strong><\/a> nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/em><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_17702\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-17702\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-17702 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/IMG_0067-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-17702\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed n\u00e1o nhi\u1ec7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng Hoa H\u1ed3ng trong Ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc 2023<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Ch\u00fac c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n t\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean kh\u00f3a 15 t\u00e2m th\u1ebf v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o n\u0103m h\u1ecdc m\u1edbi 2023-2024 trong ni\u1ec1m vui v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hi v\u1ecdng m\u1edbi.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Ch\u00fac m\u1eebng c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh T\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4. Hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c T\u00e2n Thadoers s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng n\u0103m th\u00e1ng thanh xu\u00e2n th\u1eadt \u0111\u1eb9p, th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft v\u00e0 th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb c\u00f9ng TDD.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00f9ng nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac ghi l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc v\u1eeba qua:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/_et08dhLgEI\" width=\"560\" height=\"314\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><\/iframe><\/p>\n<blockquote><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">M\u1ecdi th\u00f4ng tin th\u1eafc m\u1eafc vui l\u00f2ng g\u1eedi v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9:<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>V\u0103n ph\u00f2ng Trung t\u00e2m Tuy\u1ec3n sinh<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u1ea7ng 1, Nh\u00e0 A, <strong>Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u1ecba ch\u1ec9: Km15, Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ed9 32, Kim Chung, Ho\u00e0i \u0110\u1ee9c, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Hotline: <strong>0934 07 8668 \u2013 0243 386 1601<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Website: <strong><a href=\"http:\/\/nhaphoc.thanhdo.edu.vn\">http:\/\/nhaphoc.thanhdo.edu.vn<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><